
Array
=============
Array is static data structure
Array is implemented in java as Object
Array store same type data and are always fixed in size
Collection of similar type of data we can hold using array
Array is collection of data and Object
Array stores data as per index value
Array index always starts with 0
Array doesn't provide any method
To calculate length we have length variable in array



Types of Array
=====================
1.Single dimensional array-[]
array store data in continues locations

2.Multi-dimensional array
array store data in row and column wise

Ways of Array declaration[row][col]
=================================
1.Using new keyword
=====================
Syntax
==========
datatype array_name[]=new datatype[size]

int sid[]=new int[5];




2.Using literals(constant value)












